From 7d9715f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Windows HIP Build <build@local>
Date: 2026-06-09
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Add cudaEventCreate mapping for HIP compatibility

HIP on Windows does not define cudaEventCreate as a macro.
Add the mapping to hip.h so that llama-server can create
GPU events for timing and synchronization.

diff --git a/ggml/src/ggml-cuda/vendors/hip.h b/ggml/src/ggml-cuda/vendors/hip.h
index 1234567..abcdefg 100644
--- a/ggml/src/ggml-cuda/vendors/hip.h
+++ b/ggml/src/ggml-cuda/vendors/hip.h
@@ -XX,6 +XX,7 @@
 #define cudaFuncAttributeMaxDynamicSharedMemorySizeBytes hipFuncAttributeMaxDynamicSharedMemorySizeBytes
+#define cudaEventCreate hipEventCreate
 
 // Additional Windows HIP compatibility
 // min/max not defined in device scope on Windows